---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Tax + Accounting Services - Proactive Accounting & Tax"
  description="Tax preparation, proactive tax planning, accounting, and business advisory for individuals and small business owners in the San Diego area — services designed to reduce stress, not create it."
  path="/tax-accounting-services/"
  ogDescription="Designed to reduce stress — not create it."
  ogImage="https://proactive-at.com/assets/img/IMG_Services_first_1400.webp"
>
  <!-- ======================= Page hero ======================= -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Tax + Accounting Services</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======================= Intro ======================= -->
  <section class="split split--tight">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="split-col">
        <h2>Designed to reduce stress &mdash; not create it</h2>
        <div class="rich-text">
          <p>At Proactive Accounting &amp; Tax, we help individuals and small business owners in the San Diego area stay compliant, plan ahead, and feel confident about their financial decisions.</p>
          <p>Our services are intentionally connected.<br>Because tax preparation, bookkeeping, and planning only work when they inform each other.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="split-col split-media">
        <img src="/assets/img/IMG_Services_first_1400.webp" alt="CPA meeting with a small business client" width="700" height="700" loading="lazy">
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======================= Philosophy ======================= -->
  <section class="center-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-heading">A different kind of CPA relationship</h2>
      <div class="rich-text">
        <p>Other accounting firms treat services as separate transactions.</p>
        <p>We don&rsquo;t.</p>
        <p>We look at the full picture &mdash; your income, your business structure, your books, and your goals &mdash; and help you make better decisions before deadlines, penalties, or surprises show up.</p>
        <p>Whether you need straightforward tax support or ongoing guidance, our work is grounded in proactive planning, clear communication, and steady follow-through.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======================= Tax Preparation & Compliance ======================= -->
  <section class="split split--inner">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="split-col">
        <p class="eyebrow">Accurate, timely, and handled without panic</p>
        <h2 class="heading-sm">Tax Preparation &amp; Compliance</h2>
        <div class="rich-text">
          <p>We provide professional tax preparation services for individuals and business owners in the San Diego area &mdash; and in all 50 states &mdash; who want their returns handled carefully and correctly.</p>
          <p>This includes:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Individual and business tax returns</li>
            <li>Federal and state compliance</li>
            <li>IRS and state correspondence support</li>
            <li>Filing handled on time, with no last-minute scrambling</li>
          </ul>
          <p>Tax preparation is essential &mdash; but it&rsquo;s only one part of a healthy tax strategy. Our goal is to make filing the easy part, not the stressful one.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="split-col split-media">
        <img src="/assets/img/IMG_Services_Compliance_1000x812.webp" alt="Reviewing a completed tax return" width="500" height="406" loading="lazy">
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======================= Proactive Tax Planning ======================= -->
  <section class="split split--inner linetop">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="split-col">
        <p class="eyebrow">Make decisions before they become expensive</p>
        <h2 class="heading-sm">Proactive Tax Planning</h2>
        <div class="rich-text">
          <p>Tax planning is where most savings &mdash; and peace of mind &mdash; actually come from.</p>
          <p>As a San Diego area CPA firm, we work with clients year-round to identify opportunities, reduce tax liability legally, and plan ahead as income, business structure, or life circumstances change.</p>
          <p>Tax planning may include:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Timing income and expenses strategically</li>
            <li>Identifying deductions and credits early</li>
            <li>Planning for growth, investments, or major changes</li>
            <li>Avoiding surprises at filing time</li>
          </ul>
          <p>If your CPA only talks to you once a year, that&rsquo;s reactive.<br>We believe planning should happen before the deadline.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="split-col split-media">
        <img src="/assets/img/IMG_Services_Planning_1400.webp" alt="Planning session over financial projections" width="700" height="700" loading="lazy">
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======================= Accounting & Bookkeeping ======================= -->
  <section class="split split--inner linetop">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="split-col">
        <p class="eyebrow">Clean books that support better tax decisions</p>
        <h2 class="heading-sm">Accounting &amp; Bookkeeping</h2>
        <div class="rich-text">
          <p>Accounting shouldn&rsquo;t exist in a vacuum.</p>
          <p>We offer accounting and bookkeeping services in the San Diego area that are directly connected to your tax strategy &mdash; not just monthly reports that no one explains.</p>
          <p>Our bookkeeping support helps:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Keep records accurate and organized</li>
            <li>Reduce year-end cleanup</li>
            <li>Improve visibility into your numbers</li>
            <li>Support smarter tax planning</li>
          </ul>
          <p>This is especially helpful for business owners who feel behind, overwhelmed, or unsure if their books are telling the full story.</p>
          <p>No judgment &mdash; just structure and clarity.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="split-col split-media">
        <img src="/assets/img/IMG_Approach_bookkeeping_1400.webp" alt="Organized bookkeeping records" width="700" height="700" loading="lazy">
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======================= Business Advisory & Entity Structuring ======================= -->
  <section class="split split--inner linetop">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="split-col">
        <p class="eyebrow">Think through decisions &mdash; not just report on them</p>
        <h2 class="heading-sm">Business Advisory &amp; Entity Structuring</h2>
        <div class="rich-text">
          <p>As your business grows, the decisions get more complex &mdash; and the tax impact matters.</p>
          <p>We provide advisory support around:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>LLC vs. S-Corp considerations</li>
            <li>Business structure changes</li>
            <li>Owner compensation planning</li>
            <li>Strategic decisions that affect taxes</li>
          </ul>
          <p>This service is ideal for business owners who want a CPA that helps them think through decisions &mdash; not just report on them afterward.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="split-col split-media">
        <img src="/assets/img/IMG_Services_structure_1400.webp" alt="Advising on business structure options" width="700" height="700" loading="lazy">
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
